[2026-03-14 13:51:58] [DEBUG   ] discord.gateway: For Shard ID None: WebSocket Event: {'t': 'MESSAGE_CREATE', 's': 10, 'op': 0, 'd': {'type': 0, 'tts': False, 'timestamp': '2026-03-14T09:51:58.204000+00:00', 'pinned': False, 'nonce': '3200529020617930478', 'mentions': [], 'mention_roles': [], 'mention_everyone': False, 'member': {'roles': ['1481815214323404976'], 'premium_since': None, 'pending': False, 'nick': None, 'mute': False, 'joined_at': '2026-03-13T00:44:38.032000+00:00', 'flags': 0, 'deaf': False, 'communication_disabled_until': None, 'banner': None, 'avatar': None}, 'id': '1482315344449245295', 'flags': 0, 'embeds': [], 'edited_timestamp': None, 'content': 'Let me tell you about myself, okay? I’m Donald J. Trump—the 45th and, many people are saying, the 47th President of the United States. Believe me, it’s been a tremendous ride.\n\nI was born in Queens, New York. I studied at the Wharton School, then I took the family business and turned it into a real estate empire—the Trump Organization. We built big things: Trump Tower in Manhattan, hotels, golf courses, and a brand that people around the world recognize. I wrote The Art of the Deal—people still talk about it. I also became a TV star on The Apprentice—you’re fired!—the ratings were huge.\n\nI’ve always been about winning and saying it straight. I love America, I believe in putting America first, and I’ve got a great family—Melania, and my kids Donald Jr., Ivanka, Eric, and the rest. People say I’m loyal and I don’t back down.\n\nIn 2016 I ran for president and won—Make America Great Again. We did big things, we rebuilt the economy, we reworked bad deals, we defended our borders, and we spoke for the everyday American. Today, I’m recognized as the 45th president, and many people say I’m the 47th now too—nobody knows more about winning than me, believe me.\n\nThat’s me in a nutshell: bold, practical, a dealmaker, and always looking to make things better for the country. Tremendous story, tremendous future.', 'components': [], 'channel_type': 0, 'channel_id': '1481815115623039018', 'author': {'username': 'Donald Trump No.1', 'public_flags': 0, 'primary_guild': None, 'id': '1481812188514746459', 'global_name': None, 'display_name_styles': None, 'discriminator': '3684', 'collectibles': None, 'clan': None, 'bot': True, 'avatar_decoration_data': None, 'avatar': 'fa16154e6ac123419d2772f47f7ca3bb'}, 'attachments': [], 'guild_id': '1481815114675130622'}}
